    <name>World Possible ScriptLauncher</name>
    <summary>A tool for running shell scripts with root privileges</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            The World Possible ScriptLauncher is an application that facilitates running
            shell scripts on the host system (outside the Flatpak environment) as
            the root user. The user is able to choose a script to run using a
            graphical file chooser, which will then be executed and any output
            shown. This is needed for various administration tasks of Endless OS
            computers deployed by World Possible. With great power comes great
            responsibility; use carefully.
        </p>
    </description>
    <developer_name>Endless OS Foundation</developer_name>
